                    <h3 class="mod" data-uuid="cd77cc3bcc3e4c3a8441088339b22e3b">Forming a Government, 1775–1791</h3>
                    <p class="mod" data-uuid="96839e4b1d424ec5a7e754206945e5a8">The United States developed rapidly in its first
                        25 years as a nation. The colonies organized a government, discovered the
                        weaknesses of that government, and compromised to peacefully create a new government.
                        The United States also began to interact as an equal with foreign nations.</p>
